## Common Patterns

### Task Submission
1. Create wrapper script with task details
2. Submit to scheduler/platform
3. Monitor task status
4. Collect results and logs

### Resource Management
- CPU allocation
- Memory requirements
- Time limits
- Queue/partition selection

### Error Handling
- Exit code checking
- Log collection
- Retry logic
- Resource cleanup
